---

## When Reporting Issues

Please include the following to help us assist you faster:

- **Device model** (e.g. iPhone 15, Samsung Galaxy S24)
- **Operating system version** (e.g. iOS 18.2, Android 15)
- **App version** (shown in Settings within the app)
- **Description of the issue** (what happened, when it happened, steps to reproduce if possible)

---

## Common Topics

- **Gameplay questions** — How to play, tips, level help
- **Technical problems** — Crashes, freezes, display issues
- **In-app purchases** — Purchase not received, restore purchases
- **Account / progress** — Lost progress, leaderboard issues
- **Ads** — Ad-related issues (or purchase "Remove Ads" to disable them)

